abstract: >-
  A domain-agnostic framework for ensuring data integrity in high-velocity, 
  volatile telemetry environments. It implements a heuristic control plane 
  for identifying and repairing schema drift in real-time, validated against 
  synthetic F1 racing data and clinical HL7 streams.
